2. Confirm architecture & flows with `docs/architecture-summary.md` and `docs/detailed-architecture.md`.
3. Review implementation conventions in `docs/development-playbook.md`.
4. Consult integration specifics (Canva, Gemini, n8n, Remotion Worker, social platforms) as needed.

